videos.description: Kyrie Irving knocks down a tough jumper from the corner and then Kevin Durant hits a jumper of his own on the next possession.

videos.headline: Kyrie and KD drain back-to-back tough jumpers

videos.description: Khris Middleton hands the ball off to Giannis Antetokounmpo, who rises up for a two-handed jam.

videos.headline: Giannis gets in for the easy dunk

videos.description: Khris Middleton knocks down a 3-pointer, then the Bucks get a quick steal which leads to Brook Lopez also hitting a 3-pointer.

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo grabs a defensive board and drives all the way tp the bucket for a one-handed dunk.
